{"title":"Git常用命令小记","slug":"Git常用命令小记","date":"2016-10-04T16:22:00.000Z","updated":"2026-02-08T11:30:13.899Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Git常用命令小记.json","excerpt":"Git的使用确实要比SVN复杂，下面记录了一下Git的常用命令，以备以后查用。","covers":null,"content":"<p>Git的使用确实要比SVN复杂，下面记录了一下Git的常用命令，以备以后查用。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h2 id=\"%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E7%9B%91%E8%A7%86%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" tabindex=\"-1\">排除监视文件<a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E7%9B%91%E8%A7%86%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>在代码库根目录添加一个<code>.gitignore</code>文件，在文件中写上文件名（含路径）或路径名即可</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA\" tabindex=\"-1\">新建<a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>新建一个代码库</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git init &lt;repo&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>克隆一个项目</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git clone [url]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\" tabindex=\"-1\">配置<a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>显示当前配置</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git config --list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>编辑配置文件</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git config -e &lt;--global&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>设置用户信息</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git config &lt;--global&gt; user.name &quot;[name]&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ git config &lt;--global&gt; user.email &quot;[email]&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%2F%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4\" tabindex=\"-1\">添加/删除<a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%2F%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>添加指定文件到暂存区</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git add [file]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>添加指定目录到暂存区，包含子目录</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git add [dir]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>添加当前目录的所有文件到暂存区</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git add .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>未完待续…</p>\n</blockquote>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex/dist/katex.min.css\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/markdown-it-texmath/css/texmath.min.css\">\n","more":"<h2 id=\"%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E7%9B%91%E8%A7%86%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" tabindex=\"-1\">排除监视文件<a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E7%9B%91%E8%A7%86%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>在代码库根目录添加一个<code>.gitignore</code>文件，在文件中写上文件名（含路径）或路径名即可</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA\" tabindex=\"-1\">新建<a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#%E6%96%B0%E5%BB%BA\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>新建一个代码库</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git init &lt;repo&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>克隆一个项目</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git clone [url]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\" tabindex=\"-1\">配置<a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>显示当前配置</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git config --list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>编辑配置文件</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git config -e &lt;--global&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>设置用户信息</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git config &lt;--global&gt; user.name &quot;[name]&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$ git config &lt;--global&gt; user.email &quot;[email]&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%2F%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4\" tabindex=\"-1\">添加/删除<a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%2F%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>添加指定文件到暂存区</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git add [file]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>添加指定目录到暂存区，包含子目录</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git add [dir]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>添加当前目录的所有文件到暂存区</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ git add .</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<blockquote>\n<p>未完待续…</p>\n</blockquote>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex/dist/katex.min.css\">\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/markdown-it-texmath/css/texmath.min.css\">","categories":[{"name":"技术","path":"api/categories/技术.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Git","path":"api/tags/Git.json"}]}